(80, 'widget_text', 'a:3:{i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:1080:"<div class="index_about_mayor "><p>Just over three years ago, you elected me to be your mayor with an overwhelming majority and with a mandate for change.</p><p class="top_padding">There was an increasing sense that City Hall had become an insiders club and that decisions were made behind closed doors.</p><p  class="top_padding">Voters asked me to make our city government more open and accountable, and to ensure we address our highest priorities.</p><p  class="top_padding">Im proud to say Ive kept my promises to you. Ive ensured accountability and delivered results.</p><p class="top_padding">Were on the right path of positive change. Weve made tremendous progress. Weve promoted record job growth. We have a plan for our future. And were in the process of laying the foundation for even greater things in the next four years.</p><p class="top_padding">Lets continue to work together to make Columbus an even safer, stronger and more prosperous city!</p>\r\n        <div class="mayor_name full_width">- Kristen  </div>\r\n      </div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:49:" 2015 Mayor Kristen Brown, All Rights Reserved.";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
