(222, 1, '2015-01-15 01:40:50', '2015-01-15 01:40:50', '<div class="main_heading full_width top_margin">\n<h1 class="red_color ">Encouraged Job Growth</h1>\n<div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\n<p class="top_margin">Under Mayor Kristen Browns leadership, Columbus has set records for the number of jobs and employment. The Columbus metropolitan area is at all-time record highs for both the number of jobs in our community  more than 51,000 - and the number of residents who are employed  more than 41,000. Our unemployment rate is currently the second lowest in the state.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width btm_padding1 "><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-535" src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/jobs1.png" alt="jobs" width="1001" height="320" /></div>\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\n<ul>\n	<li>2,500 more jobs were created and nearly 3,500 more residents are employed in our community than three years ago.</li>\n	<li>Our largest employer, Cummins Inc., announced they would begin engine production at the Columbus Engine Plant again and add another 500 well-paying jobs to our community. Cummins announcement was a resounding reaffirmation of Cummins strong commitment to Columbus, Indiana.</li>\n	<li>Provided tax incentives, encouraging the creation and retention of more than another 600 jobs and investments exceeding $250 million.</li>\n	<li>Developed a preliminary plan to redevelop the nearly 700 acres</span> of the former Walesboro Airport into an industrial park to provide shovel-ready industrial sites for continued job-creating growth.</li>\n	<li>Developed the citys first Strategic Growth Plan to readily and efficiently accommodate the citys growth outside todays city limits.</li>\n	<li>Formed a public-private partnership to develop a 114-bed, $5 million student housing complex at the airport. This is the game-changer for our four colleges recruitment efforts and our ability to produce a steady pipeline of skilled and educated workers that our employers need to prosper.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Jobs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '174-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-15 01:40:50', '2015-01-15 01:40:50', '', 174, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/174-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
