ies and equipment, saving taxpayers more than a million dollars a year.  </li>\r\n<li>Saved more than $500,000 annually by decreasing taxpayers share of rising employee health care costs.</li>\r\n<li>Terminated the personal use of city vehicles except for police and fire.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\r\n<h2>Maintained Financial Strength</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Issued no incremental new debt and maintained healthy cash reserves.</li>\r\n<li>Maintained Standard and Poors very strong credit rating of a AA-.\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Fiscal Responsibility', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-14 08:45:55', '2015-01-14 08:45:55', '', 178, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/178-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(605, 1, '2015-01-14 08:48:35', '2015-01-14 08:48:35', '<div class="main_heading full_width">\r\n  <h1 class="red_color ">You Can Help</h1>\r\n  <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin ">\r\n<p class="btm_padding1 " >Together, we took back our community in the mayors race in 2011.  In the Republican primary on this May 5th, the choices are clear.  We can go back to politics as usual and taking your tax dollars or we can continue to positively change our governments course, protect your tax dollars and advance Columbus toward our vision.  </p>\r\n<p  >But we need you again to make it happen and we hope youll join our team.  \r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 'You Can Help', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-14 08:48:35', '2015-01-14 08:48:35', '', 16, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
