adding">\r\n<h2 >A Proven, Qualified Leader</h2>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width top_padding"><img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/about_img21.png" alt="about_img2" width="1001" height="320" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-486" /></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Prior to serving as Mayor, Mayor Brown came from a successful career in business, holding numerous positions of increasing responsibility in the fields of banking, investment management and the computer software industry.  Brown was a senior executive and Vice President of several leading companies including publicly-traded giants Oracle and Intuit, the developer of Quickbooks, Quicken and TurboTax.</li>\r\n<li>Brown graduated at the top of her class from Columbus North High School in 1982. She graduated from Brown University with a B.A., magna cum laude, in 1986 and from Harvard University with an M.B.A in 1993.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'About Kristen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-14 09:06:35', '2015-01-14 09:06:35', '', 14, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(612, 1, '2015-01-14 09:10:45', '2015-01-14 09:10:45', '<div class="main_heading full_width top_margin">\r\n  <h1>Made Columbus Safer, Protected You and Your Family  </h1>\r\n  <div class="main_headingBorder"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width top_margin">\r\n    <p class="btm_padding1">Along with maintaining and improving our public infrastructure, public safety is job number one for Mayor Kristen Brown. </p>\r\n<h2 >Accelerated Law Enforcement Efforts</h2>\r\n<p class="btm_padding1">Under Mayor Browns leadership, we have more police officers on our streets than at any time in our citys history and never before have they been more productive. </p>    \r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="img_container"><img src="http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/safety1.png" alt="safety" width="609" height="307" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-549" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Choked the flow of dangerous drugs into our community by cracking down on a threefold increase in the number of dealers of methamphetamine and heroin. .</li>\r\n<li>Restored stability to our hardest-hit neighborhoods with a 45% increase in community policing patrols and a new dedicated community policing unit.  </li>\r\n<li>Cut violent crime nearly in half and cut property crime by 23%.Reduced the number of traffic accidents through an acceleration of traffic enforcement efforts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\r\n<h2>Improved Emergency Medical Services and Saved Tax Dollars</h2>\r\n<p>Mayor Kristen Brown and her team have significantly advanced emergency medical services, ensuring residents have the best chance for surviving a life-threatening event. </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Awarded a new ambulance contract to Columbus Regional Hospital after conducting a fair, transparent and competitive bidding process resulting in significantly improved service and reduced costs to taxpayers from nearly $1 million every year to $0 a year.</li>\r\n<li>Increased the number of paramedic firefighters certified in advanced life-support techniques to staff one on all six engines at every fire station every day.  </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="inner_text_container full_width">\r\n<h2>Improved Rescue, Disaster and Extreme Weather Response</h2>\r\n<p>Mayor Kristen Brown and her team have ensured that we are well prepared for the myriad of threats our community faces.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sold the mayors city-owned vehicle to fund ice water rescue equipment for City firefighters to ensure optimal victim survivability around the citys 161 ponds and lakes.</li>\r\n<li>Unveiled the first-ever Flood Risk Warning and Management Plan on the fifth anniversary of the 2008 flood. Never again will we be unprepared.</li>\r\n<li>Deployed an emergency notification system that sends alerts to citizens by voicemail, text messages and emails during emergencies. </li>\r\n<li>Ensured that our roads were cleared of snow and ice and potholes were patched in a timely manner during extreme winter weather the last two years.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Public Safety', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '170-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-14 09:10:45', '2015-01-14 09:10:45', '', 170, 'http://localhost/brown-for-columbus/170-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
